<h1 align="center">Solis AI</h1>

<p align="center">
Video repurposing system for transforming long-form content into structured, reusable video outputs using template-based generation.
</p>

<p align="center">
Upload a YouTube video. Solis AI extracts structure, segments content, and generates new formats using customizable templates.
</p>

---

## Overview

Solis AI converts unstructured video content into structured media assets through automated analysis and template-driven rendering.

The system focuses on scalability, consistency, and reusability of generated content.

---

## Pipeline

Input → Ingestion → Analysis → Segmentation → Structuring → Template Mapping → Output Generation

---

## Core Capabilities

- YouTube video ingestion and processing  
- Automated content segmentation  
- Structural extraction of topics and scenes  
- Template-based video reconstruction  
- Multi-format output generation  

---

## Design System

Solis AI uses a consistent visual token system across all outputs:

- Primary color: `#f97316`
- Accent: `#c2410c`
- Surface: soft translucent layers
- Text: high-contrast neutral ink system
- Gradients: warm orange spectrum

---

## Philosophy

Solis AI is built on three principles:

- Structure over randomness  
- Templates over manual editing  
- Reusable systems over one-off outputs  

---

## Status

Active development
